additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: INGREDIENTS: Beef Bolognese Sauce (40%) [Australian No Added Hormone Beef (33%), Diced Tomato (31.5%) (Tomato, Acidity Regulator (330), Mineral Salt (509)), Water, Tomato Paste, Celery, Onion, Carrot, Red Wine (1.0%), Vegetable Oil, Thickener (Starch), Crushed Garlic, Beef Flavoured Seasoning (contains Flavourings, Natural Colours (150a, Turmeric)), Salt, Thyme, Oregano, Modified Starch (1422, 1442)], Cooked Rigatoni Pasta (30%) [Pasta (Durum Wheat, Durum Wheat Semolina), Vegetable Oil], Cheese Sauce (21%) [Milk, Cream (Milk), Water, Cheddar Cheese (Milk) (9%), Thickener (Starch), Salted Butter (Milk), Parmesan Cheese (Milk), Vegetable Stock Seasoning (contains Natural Flavouring), Dijon Mustard, Natural Cheese Flavour (Milk), Salt, Natural Preservative (234), Modified Starch (1422, 1442)], Cheese Topping (8%) [Cheddar Cheese (60%) (Milk, Salt, Starter Culture (Milk), Rennet, Tapioca Starch, Anticaking Agent (460), Preservative (200), Lipase), Mozzarella Cheese (Milk) (40%)].

description: From our kitchen to yours. So you can experience the food of Italy at home we take durum wheat pasta and match to delicious simmered sauces before finishing with cheese. Food that is full of flavour and ready for you in minutes
name: Kitchen Bolognese Bake
